David Juarez:

""Based in Barcelona, Straddle3 is a multidisciplinary collective that works in open source urban projects, like transformation of vacant urban lots into community spaces, DIY houses built out of recycled materials, participatory social/cultural facilities or free software tools for collaborative urban action. We are founder members of Arquitecturas Colectivas Network." 
(Commonswatch, December 2016)

